{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparison-with-the-inequality-operator","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Poredjenje sa Operatorom Nejednakosti","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Operator nejednakosti (<code>!=</code>) je suprotnost operatoru jednakosti. Nejednakost znaci nije jednako. Operator nejednakosti vraca <code>false</code> kada bi operator jednakosti vratio <code>true</code>, i obrnuto. Kao i operator jednakosti, operator nejednakosti konvertuje tipove podataka tokom poredjenja.</p>\n<p><strong>Primeri</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">1 !=  2    // true\n1 != \"1\"   // false\n1 != '1'   // false\n1 != true  // false\n0 != false // false\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244d2","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Dodajte operator nejednakosti <code>!=</code> u <code>if</code> izraz tako da funkcija vraca string <code>Not Equal</code> kada <code>val</code> nije jednako <code>99</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16787,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparison-with-the-inequality-operator"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"// Setup\nfunction testNotEqual(val) {\n  if (val) { // Change this line\n    return \"Not Equal\";\n  }\n  return \"Equal\";\n}\n\ntestNotEqual(10);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>testNotEqual(99)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Equal</code></p>","tes